Native compilation:

1) apt-get update

2) apt-get install libncurses-dev

3) download the kernel source code from https://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v3.x

4) tar -xvf linux-3.19.8.tar.gz

5) cd linux-3.19.8/

6) make menuconfig

7) make

8) make modules

9) make modules_install

10) make install

11) reboot
